item.description:
First on the Metaviz landing page click &ldquo;Start App&rdquo;
Next scroll to the bottom and select &ldquo;ibd_biopsy_hmp2data&rdquo; Choose &ldquo;Add Visualization&rdquo; and click &ldquo;Heatmap&rdquo;&quot;
On the Heatmap click the Settings icon (middle) and in the Settings menu change &ldquo;Plot Label&rdquo; dropdown menu from &ldquo;name&rdquo; to &ldquo;diagnosis&rdquo; and toggle the button for &ldquo;Row labels as color&rdquo; to &ldquo;On&rdquo;
Select samples to visualize and click &ldquo;Ok&rdquo;
Choose &ldquo;Add visualization&rdquo; click &ldquo;Diversity Box Plot&rdquo;
